{"tid":1832530,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"面對武漢肺炎疫情 有小巴營運商已即時暫停往返西九高鐵站的小巴服務","createTime":"2020-01-21T08:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T10:32:44.000Z","uid":28114,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"88c24c5db7bc65377c0fe4db8cbad0d688b11e20","tid":1832530,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:39:51.000Z","msg":"【#特別車務消息】鑑於「武漢肺炎」，即「嚴重新型傳染性病原體呼吸系統病」疫情已趨嚴峻，本公司考慮到車長及乘客的健康安全風險，尤其是車長的職業健康安全問題，即時起暫停Rt. 6 繞經西九龍高鐵站的特別班次，直至疫情穩定為止，敬請 貴客留意。<br />\n<br />\n另外，本公司將進一步加強車廂、冷氣系統的清潔消毒工作，並已備有口罩供車長及站務員配戴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YgHe49v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYgHe49v.jpg&h=313a6bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/723556761026523/posts/2570656036316577/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F723556761026523%2Fposts%2F2570656036316577%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=0618f653\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/723556761026523/posts/2570656036316577/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"c433aaf2693fc4301dd1b618ce2fc18827f09064","tid":1832530,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedcca60a0c27fab356552dfa64a8de3d728595f","tid":1832530,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63636f57a97b8d364fcfb0629e7649adc879b599","tid":1832530,"uid":207614,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:43:58.000Z","msg":"點解呀 驚咩呀"},{"pid":"2f78703fbeab27ed84bf3eeb50e6cf833a60f77f","tid":1